import React from 'react'

import Blog from './pages/Blog'
import About from './pages/About'
import MainPage from './pages/MainPage'
import Portfolio from './pages/Portfolio'
import ContactPage from './pages/ContactPage'
import Header from './components/Header/Header'
import Footer from './components/Footer/Footer'
import BlogsMenu from './components/BlogsMenu/BlogsMenu'

import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route } from 'react-router-dom'


const App = () => {

  return (
    <Router>
        <Header />
        <Route path='/blog' component={BlogsMenu} />
        {/* <Route path='/about' component={About} /> */}
        <Route path='/' exact component={MainPage} />
        {/* <Route path='/contact' component={ContactPage} /> */}
        <Route path='https://themeforest.net/item/snow-minimal-clean-wordpress-portfolio-theme/19347252?ref=unvab' component={Portfolio} />
        <Footer />
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
